Package: rssistat
Type: Package
Title: ISTAT RSS Feed Discovery and Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Giampaolo Montaletti", email = "giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Discover and analyze RSS feeds from ISTAT (Italian National
    Institute of Statistics) website. Provides tools for scanning web pages
    to find RSS/Atom feed URLs, parsing feed content, and summarizing news.
